'''Jere''' ɗun hukuma pamarun e diiwal Borno gal Najeriya. Hautorde magal eder gelle khaddamari.

== Mangu Gelle ==
Egal wodii geɓal ba 868km2. 
== Ɗuɗirka ==
E ɗuɗirka yimɓe 211,204 e limgal 2006 ɓurgal ɗuɗuki yimɓe e gelle Jere (larabanko’en baggara). Lamba wuro figirgo go geɓal gal hanjum woonii 600.<ref>http://www.nipost.gov.ng/PostCode.aspx | accessdate = 2009-10-20 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121126042849/http://www.nipost.gov.ng/postcode.aspx | archivedate = 2012-11-26}}</ref> 
== Habaru Gelle ==
Egal go’o eɗer hukumaji pamari sappo e jewe go’o latiɗe e lamarde Borno. Diiwal undiiwal gal yimɓe ɗenno galɗe [[Diiwal Borno]] e [[Naajeeriya]].
